flowchart TD
    A[User opens /tasks list view] --> B[API reads projected task summaries]
    B --> C[List renders owner metadata per row]
    C --> D{Owner filter selected?}
    D -- No --> E[Show full result set]
    D -- Specific owner --> F[Show matching owner rows]
    D -- Unassigned --> G[Show only unassigned rows]
    F --> H[User clears filter]
    G --> H
    H --> E
    I[PM reassigns task in detail view] --> J[Assignment event updates projected current owner]
    J --> K[User refreshes or reloads /tasks]
    K --> L[List shows updated owner]
